This is a quick reminder that <%= full_and_preferred_patient_name %> may get their <%= vaccination %> at <%= location_name %> on <%= next_session_date %>.  <%= subsequent_session_dates_offered_message %>

If you haven’t already told <%= short_patient_name %> that they’ll be vaccinated, please let them know what to expect.

If <%= short_patient_name_apos %> health changes, or you arrange for them to be vaccinated elsewhere, please contact us. You should also contact us to ask about alternative sessions if <%= short_patient_name %> is absent or unwell on the day of the vaccination session. You can email <%= subteam_email %> or phone <%= subteam_phone %>.

<% if vaccine_is?("injection") %>##Helping the session run smoothly

It’s helpful for your child to wear a short-sleeved shirt on the day of the vaccination to give us easy access to the arm.

It’s also helpful for them to have breakfast, as this reduces the likelihood of fainting.<% end %>

<% if vaccine_is?("nasal") %>^If your child has asthma, please let us know if they’ve had a flare-up of asthma symptoms in the 3 days before the vaccination is due to take place, or on the day of the vaccination. This includes wheezing or needing to use a reliever inhaler more than usual.<% end %>

